My collection of fortune cookies
How to install:
	$ git clone https://github.com/rjcoelho/fortune.git .
	$ cd fortune
	$ sudo ln -s `pwd`/pragmatic /usr/share/games/fortunes/pramatic
	$ sudo ln -s `pwd`/pragmatic.dat /usr/share/games/fortunes/pramatic.dat
How to add new fortune cookies:
	* write a text file with % seperating cookies
	$ strfile cookiefile 
